                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis" style="color:#fc81cd;">Professional<br /> Community</h3>
                    <p>Join a community of verified professionals and clients. Build your reputation and grow your business with us.</p>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</section>
<section id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action mt-1" style="">Sign up and create your profile.</a>
            <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action mt-1" style="">Browse projects or post your own.</a>
            <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action mt-1" style="">Engage with clients or freelancers and start your project.</a>
            <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action mt-1" style="">Use our smart contracts to ensure secure payments upon project completion.</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="contact" class="contact py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-center">Have questions? Reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:support@freelanceexchange.com">support@freelanceexchange.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    section {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .navbar {
        background-color: #fc81cd;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
        
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .hero {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }

        .hero h1 {
            color: #fc81cd;
        }

    .features .card-title, .how-it-works .text-center {
        color: #fc81cd;
    }

    .btn-primary {
        background-color: #fc81cd;
        border-color: #fc81cd;
    }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #e170b6;
            border-color: #e170b6;
        }

</style>

